\pard\plain \tx1123\tx1685\tx2246\tx2794\tx3355\tx3917\tx4478\tx5040\tx5602\tx6163\tx6725\fi720\ri-720\sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 From behind came the sound of stone sliding against stone. Torchlight flooded into the cramped cave as the heavy stone door opened. A short and stout Jandri man bumbled in, hunched over. When he saw Mandri sitting up, staring at him, he nearly dropped his torch. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Shoulda told he woke up!\u8221\'94 he shouted as he set his glare upon Seb.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93He woke up,\u8221\'94 Seb replied with a wry grin. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri, feeling lively, said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You must be Hill.\u8221\'94}}